'''Afus''' d agman (organe) gar yegmanen n [[Amdan|wemdan]], yezga-d deg taggara n yiɣil. Yal amdan ɣur-s sin (2) n yifasen, '''afus ayfus''' akked '''ufus aẓelmaḍ''', yal afus ɣur-s semmus (5) n [[Aḍad|yiḍudan]], s yessen yezmer umdan ad yeg aṭas n tigawin (ad yeṭṭef, ad yaru ...) neɣ ad yemmeslay (tutlayt n usekni). Afus d allal yesɛan azal ameqran ɣer wemdan
